title: Wall Street Breakfast June 27: Russia Defaults on Foreign Debt for the First Time Since 1918
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Russia defaults on foreign debt for the first time since 1918. Four G7 nations to impose ban on gold bullion imports from Russia. Goldman Sachs said looking to raise $2B to buy Celsius Network assets - report. Biden unveils $600B G7 infrastructure plan to counter China. Catch today’s WSB article here.
